{[#]} 10. h4 $1 h6 {a lot of players are playing like this with Black, but now
White has the advantage:} (10... f5 $1 {Black really needs to play this move,
against Ne4 ideas and close the b1-h7 diagonal for the White queen} 11. d4
cxd4 (11... Bb7 $2 {Adhiban-So} 12. dxc5 Bxc5 13. Rd1 $16) (11... Nxc3 12. Qxc3
Bf6 13. Qc2 Bb7 14. dxc5 bxc5 15. Bc4 Qe7 16. Ng5 $14) 12. Nxd5 Qxd5 13. Bc4
Qd6 14. Rd1 $14) 11. g4 $1 Bb7 12. g5 h5 13. Rg1 Rc8 14. Ne4 $18 *

